# =============================================================================
# Release Guard -- .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# This repo is the Unity package itself (Editor/, Runtime/, Tests/,
# Documentation~/) at the root. The root is also openable as a Unity project
# for IDE support, and UnityDevHost/ is a throwaway Unity project that consumes
# the package via "file:../.." to compile and run its tests.
#
# Rules below:
#   1. Ignore all Unity/IDE-generated output anywhere in the tree.
#   2. Ignore the root Unity-project scaffolding (Assets/, ProjectSettings/,
#      Packages/) -- it is not package content and is regenerated on open.
#      UnityDevHost/ is the canonical dev/test project and IS tracked.
#   3. .meta files for package content ARE tracked (Unity requires stable
#      GUIDs across package updates). Only scaffolding/tooling metas are ignored.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Unity generated output (any project, any depth)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Ll]ibrary/
[Tt]emp/
[Oo]bj/
# Anchored to repo root: a bare "[Bb]uild/" would also ignore the package's
# legitimate Editor/Build/ source folder.
/[Bb]uild/
/[Bb]uilds/
[Ll]ogs/
[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/
[Mm]emoryCaptures/
[Rr]ecordings/
.consulo/
sysinfo.txt
crashlytics-build.properties

# Loose Unity / tooling log files (the Logs/ dirs are already covered above)
*.log

# Unity asset import / artifact databases
/[Aa]ssets/AssetStoreTools*
*.apk
*.aab
*.unitypackage
*.app

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# IDE / editor generated solution and project files
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.csproj
*.sln
*.suo
*.user
*.userprefs
*.unityproj
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.tmp

# JetBrains Rider
.idea/
*.DotSettings.user

# Visual Studio / VS Code
.vs/
.vscode/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Root Unity-project scaffolding (anchored to repo root only).
# The package lives at the root; these are NOT package content. UnityDevHost/
# is the tracked dev project, so equivalent paths there are unaffected.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
/Assets/
!/assets/
/Assets.meta
/ProjectSettings/
/ProjectSettings.meta
/Packages/
/Packages.meta
/Logs.meta
/UserSettings.meta

# Unity may generate a meta for the root release-please config when scanned; the
# repo root is not a package, so this is never tracked.
/release-please-config.json.meta

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# UnityDevHost: keep the project definition, drop generated output
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
UnityDevHost/[Ll]ibrary/
UnityDevHost/[Tt]emp/
UnityDevHost/[Oo]bj/
UnityDevHost/[Bb]uild/
UnityDevHost/[Ll]ogs/
UnityDevHost/[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# npm / Node (CI uses `npm pack` to produce the UPM tarball)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules/
*.tgz
npm-debug.log*
package-lock.json

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OS cruft
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
